There were many police vehicles, a lot of shooting, a lot of chaotic driving and crashing, and eventually they got into a different van and set the first car on fire.
response_clean: 3-4 men in creepy nun costumes and masks robbed a truck full of cash. They had big guns, maybe machine guns. They shot and killed one of the guards of the truck. They took all of the money from the truck and put it in their car and then got in a big car chase with the cops who were trying to capture them. There were many police vehicles, a lot of shooting, a lot of chaotic driving and crashing, and eventually they got into a different van and set the first car on fire.

The main sequence is accurate, but there is a factual error about the guard's fate and some minor embellishments.

The Black guy, shown in the picture, said that he only like pizza from a particular pizza restaurant that was 2 hours away, when in actuality he did not like pizza at all.  His co-worker, the white guy, drove to the restaurant that was 2 hours away, without his knowledge, and purchased the pizza for his friend.  The picture above shows the friend picking up the pizza to eat it when in actuality he was disgusted with the pizza. response_clean: A pizza contest in regards to the best pizza was orchestrated by the co-workers at the school.  Everyone was to have purchased their favorite pizza for the contest.  The Black guy, shown in the picture, said that he only like pizza from a particular pizza restaurant that was 2 hours away, when in actuality he did not like pizza at all.  His co-worker, the white guy, drove to the restaurant that was 2 hours away, without his knowledge, and purchased the pizza for his friend.  The picture above shows the friend picking up the pizza to eat it when in actuality he was disgusted with the pizza.  He told the truth to all the co-workers about not liking pizza and his friend was dismayed at him for telling a lie and requested his money back.
score_explanation: The participant accurately describes the setup (pizza contest, Gregory's fabricated story, Jacob's effort to get the pizza, and Gregory's confession). They also mention the group’s reaction and the lie being revealed. However, they miss the details about the dramatic mop drop, the Lady Gaga joke, the extended group interrogation about other foods, and Gregory fleeing the lounge. The response is detailed and mostly accurate but omits some key comedic and emotional moments.

question_text: 13. What happened in the scene? Please write a brief summary as accurately as you can. Try to include the main events and any key characters you remember. It’s okay if you don’t remember everything, just do your best.
response_raw: 3 men put on masks with nun habits in a car. One little boy sees one of them and looks scared as they drive by.  They proceeded to rob a armored bank truck, shoot at pedestrians to keep them back. One of the main characters shot a cop/guard that was sneaking around the side. The driver has a police radio tracker waiting for it to be called in and telling them their time. They pack duffle bags full of cash and throw them into the trunk of the car. The other two are mad he shot him. Then they are in a getaway chase and start shooting at other cop cars to try to get away. They get trapped in an alleyway, but switch to a new car with the duffles of money and set their car on fire.
response_clean: 3 men put on masks with nun habits in a car. One little boy sees one of them and looks scared as they drive by.  They proceeded to rob a armored bank truck, shoot at pedestrians to keep them back. One of the main characters shot a cop/guard that was sneaking around the side. The driver has a police radio tracker waiting for it to be called in and telling them their time. They pack duffle bags full of cash and throw them into the trunk of the car. The other two are mad he shot him. Then they are in a getaway chase and start shooting at other cop cars to try to get away. They get trapped in an alleyway, but switch to a new car with the duffles of money and set their car on fire.
score_explanation: The participant provides a highly detailed and accurate account, mentioning the nun masks, the armored truck robbery, the guard being shot, the use of a police scanner, duffel bags of cash, the police chase, gunfire, the vehicle switch, and burning the original van. Minor inaccuracies (e.g., shooting at pedestrians, a little boy watching) do not detract from the strong recall of the key model events.
